The Telegraph - Calcutta : Business

 Prudential man joins Birla group

 Mumbai, July 9 (PTI): The Aditya Birla group has appointed Ajay Srinivasan as the chief executive of financial services and director (corporate strategy and business development). Srinivasan will join the group from July 16.

 Srinivasan was earlier chief executive, fund management, Prudential Corporation Asia. He led a business that covered 10 countries and managed well over $60- billion in funds under management.

 Aditya Birla group chairman Kumar Mangalam Birla said, As the chief executive of financial services, Srinivasan will set the strategic direction and vision and provide operational leadership for the groups financial services segment. 




